l derivative terms\nrespectively in the framework of spatial covariant gravity by using the\nobservational data of GWs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Dec 2021 07:00:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2022 12:36:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-02"}
