 field. Finally, we use 3D\nRaman-sideband cooling to bring the atoms near their motional ground state,\nwhich will be central to future implementations of two-qubit gates that benefit\nfrom low motional entropy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Dec 2021 15:36:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2022 21:24:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 3 May 2023 16:41:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-04"}
